10. Our Structured Approach
10.1 Discovery & Scoping
Define project scope, risks, and compliance requirements
10.2 Site Familiarisation
Understand site-specific constraints and operational realities
10.3 Assessment & Gap Analysis
Review existing arrangements against CDM requirements
10.4 Document Development
Produce clear, compliant documentation (PCI, CPP, H&S File)
10.5 Implementation Support
Support practical application across project teams
